metadata.name: Dark Lines of London
metadata.description: The Da Vinci Code meets Timeline when a London Grad Student find himself in a race against the clock to not only find John Dee's missing grimoire, but to use it to contact Dee himself; in the process stopping a chain of events that would end the world. Spun off historical facts and characters, it is a quintessentially British time-travel story with a strong conspiracy and government cover-up twist.
